{"tid":2251550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"快必申終止煽動文字案","createTime":"2020-10-21T01:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T01:20:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5b04ae72e18e669bebd474df383efc6f9054dd47","tid":2251550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:20:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/2LNS6FUXTJAWBN3LUVHA6XKGZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2F2LNS6FUXTJAWBN3LUVHA6XKGZ4%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4Qebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=4d68d478\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2F2LNS6FUXTJAWBN3LUVHA6XKGZ4%2F&h=aa53b583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/2LNS6FUXTJAWBN3LUVHA6XKGZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n快必申終止煽動文字案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QgZf5X-fw1WiZLFT5d4l1VbY9AQ=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L6KJ45ENXZE77D6F4SPDLTE2M4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQgZf5X-fw1WiZLFT5d4l1VbY9AQ%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL6KJ45ENXZE77D6F4SPDLTE2M4.jpg&h=3ae54b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■譚得志早前被拘控煽動罪，目前還柙。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人民力量副主席「快必」譚得志早前被起訴，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n譚得志在不同案件被控煽動罪名，是次申請終止聆訊的案件，涉及今年3月和7月五次街站或遊行，譚被指發表具意圖引起憎恨或藐視政府，或激起對政府離叛，或引起香港居民之間不滿或離叛的文字。控方曾在庭上透露，涉案文字包括「光復香港」、「五大訴求」、「黑警死全家」、「7.21唔見人」等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指過度限制表達自由<br />\n<br />\n不過，涉案語句詳情並未列於控罪書，譚得志指嚴重影響他準備抗辯，以此為終止聆訊理據。此外，譚指控罪懲罰無意煽惑暴力的純粹言論，過度限制表達自由，而且「煽動意圖」涵蓋範圍不夠清晰，不符合「依法規定」的要求。案件原定下月17日再提堂，譚申請盡快處理終止聆訊申請，認為繼續檢控構成濫用程序。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC1691/20"}]}